parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Inadvertent air bag deployment can cause accidents, injuries, and fatalities. It can also lead to loss of vehicle control, especially if the air bag deploys while the vehicle is in motion.
symptoms: The air bag light remains on while driving
the driver's air bag deploys unexpectedly
the air bag sensor light remains on
the air bag warning light illuminates
indicating a malfunction within the system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the air bag to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The air bag(s) did not deploy in a crash
the seat belts did not restrain the consumer
the vehicle spun around and backed into a guard rail.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Delays or failures in repairing recalled vehicles can lead to continued safety risks for consumers.
symptoms: Parts were not available to correct the recall
the dealer was unable to honor the recall due to parts unavailability
the consumer was told to wait for parts to become available.
